Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:19.64,Default,Host,0,0,0,,Macy Baljure abruptly left\NCecile Die Twice last week,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:22.83,Default,Host,0,0,0,,but there's been no word of a press\Nconference about her departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:28.70,Default,Tim,0,0,0,,Maybe she was shocked that the new \Nmember replacing her was a CG character.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:30.30,Default,Host,0,0,0,,That's not exactly correct, Tim.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:34.09,Default,Host,0,0,0,,They're not CG characters. \NThey're called Vumans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:39.72,Default,Host,0,0,0,,Now, let's talk about this video \Nthat was leaked the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:42.39,Top Italics,Ninny,0,0,0,,So irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:47.48,Italics,Host,0,0,0,,That was the moment the group's\Nleader, Ninny, denounced Macy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:53.11,Italics,Tim,0,0,0,,Wait, "leaked"? This is from a reputable\Nsource. It was on the Realist's website.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:55.58,Italics,Host,0,0,0,,We're talking about the Realist's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.95,Italics,Host,0,0,0,,It's basically gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:03.08,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,Thank you, Elly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:06.11,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,You got mad on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:11.03,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,All for me... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:16.59,Top,Ninny,0,0,0,,Illegally rearing dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.21,Top,Chief,0,0,0,,Apparently so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:23.72,Top,Chief,0,0,0,,We got a tip that someone's doing just \Nthat in Reverse London's west district.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:25.73,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,That's huge if it's actually true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:28.60,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,But why did we get stuck with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:31.17,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:34.99,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Our job is to rear and take care of dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:38.11,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,I guess illegally reared dragons count, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:40.87,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Seriously? That seems like a reach to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:44.26,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Count yourself lucky. That "reach"\Nis putting money in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:52.64,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Hey! Come on, now. You did that on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:54.51,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Whoopsie. Did I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:59.89,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Hey, it looks like all that stuff you\Ndid yesterday didn't make the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:03.89,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Even though you saved the\Ncity from a dark dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:08.00,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Well, you're reading the\NFront London articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:11.00,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Here are the Reverse London articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:17.11,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing! It's you, Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.80,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Man, you look so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:22.73,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Uh, hello? I worked my butt off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:25.37,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Ah, found it! This is what I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:30.50,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Whoa, that was close.\NI almost forgot to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.73,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,The order came with an additional request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:42.34,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Why the heck do we have to bring you along?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:45.01,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Well, it's like the chief said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.54,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Since Balgo draws dragons toward him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:50.90,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,he's perfect for helping us find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.92,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I know that! I was in the room, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.72,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Then why are you so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.83,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I'm not mad because I didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.03,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I'm mad because I have doubts \Nabout this whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:05.96,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,If you drew the short straw and had to look\Nafter the class frog, you'd be pissed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:07.04,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Even if you still did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.70,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,That's why I'm mad right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:14.94,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Balgo, she seems to have an issue with you.\NDon't you have anything to say back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:15.94,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:21.70,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that whatever's going on\Nwith my body will help you out, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:26.82,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,And if my arms just happen to slide up\Na little, they'll brush against your boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:31.26,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Just the thought of getting to feel \Nthe warm aura of your boobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:36.07,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,I-I'm so blessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:40.86,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,You do realize that if I drop you right now,\Nyou'll probably die, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:41.82,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:50.83,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I have something to give you, Balgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:52.72,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:54.83,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,This is a Piper's mantle and pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:04:02.76,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,You'll be working with us, so the chief\Nwanted you to at least look the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:07.60,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Look the part? Could that \Npipe look any more fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:13.35,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,You sure look happy. You wanted\Nto wear one of those that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:12.25,Top,Balgo,0,0,0,,Osushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:15.36,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Of course I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:18.11,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,I mean, wearing the same thing as Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:21.86,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,It feels like Noel's holding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.21,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.49,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.87,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Well? We're in the west district now. \NDo you feel anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.12,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:37.50,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,You know! Like the presence of an\Nillegally reared dragon or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.11,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.29,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,I just naturally attract dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:47.39,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,I don't have any special ability that\Nlets me communicate with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.17,Top,Balgo,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:51.52,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Then why the hell are you \Neven here?! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.94,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,An explosion! That's pretty major, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:01.90,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:05.01,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,"Looks like it"? Aren't you going down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:09.48,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,It's out of our jurisdiction. Dealing \Nwith terrorists is the police's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.84,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Let's go. It might be a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.48,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Well said, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.79,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Even if it's not a dragon, \Nwe'll probably get points for going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.55,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Tch. Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.55,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I just have to go there, right? That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:34.28,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,This is the Realist's building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:39.17,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,You could see that from where we were.\NThat's why I didn't want to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.47,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,The Realist's? You mean the tabloid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:44.78,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.42,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,They did a piece on you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.64,Top,Mob,0,0,0,,Ninny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:51.28,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,They talk about me, like, three times\Na week. Which time do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:55.44,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,It had a video of you saying\Nsomething like, "So irritating."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:59.71,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,It made you sound like you were calling \NMacy irritating after she left the group,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:00.91,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,like you hated her and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:05.42,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Oh, that? So that's how they spun it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.32,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like anyone's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:12.69,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Well, it {\i1}is{\i0} a Saturday. Not every\Ncompany treats its workers as bad as ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:18.98,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Marshal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:24.85,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Ninny?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:26.52,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,I'm going after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.19,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,I'll come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:30.96,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, so please \Nkeep your distance, Balgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.24,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:50.76,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,So it was you I saw up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.74,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.89,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,are you doing here, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:57.11,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:00.39,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,What are you doing in Reverse London...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.41,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Macy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.63,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,This company wrote a really mean article.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:11.60,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,It said you hated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:16.46,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,No, I mean... This is the \NRealist's Reverse London HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:19.66,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,It was the Realist's in Front\NLondon who wrote that article.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.53,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Ugh, seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:27.25,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,This company always writes articles \Nthat make you look like a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.17,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,That's why I came here to destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:33.45,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,But honestly, I'm used to this\Nkinda stuff, so it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:34.93,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.43,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:40.76,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Did you cause that explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:42.87,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.20,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:47.67,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,This little one did it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.69,Italics,Ninny,0,0,0,,A dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:52.09,Italics,Ninny,0,0,0,,And it's already grown that big?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.65,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Macy... Let me take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:08:01.14,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,She's not an "it." Her name is Elly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:07.04,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd know this\Nsince you're not from Reverse London,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.92,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,but contact with a dragon is a felony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:13.05,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,As long as I keep my mouth \Nshut about this, you'll be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.26,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,so please... just let me take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.43,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.72,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I'm saying this for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.93,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,If they find out, you're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:25.57,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,The one who taught me never \Nto trust anyone who says,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:27.76,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,"I'm saying this for your sake"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:30.19,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,was you, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:37.91,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,Elly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:42.81,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,You don't look very happy\Nconsidering we found our dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:46.29,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,If I was happy after finding out\Nsomeone I knew was behind it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.79,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I'd be a psycho.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.00,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Are you Macy Baljure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:56.13,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. You don't look like how \NI'd pictured you, so I wasn't sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.68,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:08.06,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,Why are you talking like \Nyou're Nina's best friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.06,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I will murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.57,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,She's in love with me, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:18.00,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,She always gets like this any\Ntime a girl is friendly with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:21.58,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Wait... was I being friendly with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.59,Top,Macy,0,0,0,,Where the hell did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:28.09,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Anyway, the direct approach\N won't work when she's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:28.58,Top,Macy,0,0,0,,Get out here, you balloon-titted skank!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:32.94,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I'll go in from the roof.\NYou keep her distracted from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.49,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Ninny, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.41,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Ninny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.31,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:48.13,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,She flew further than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:05.45,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Banks Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:08.46,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,What brings you to the Crown Council?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:12.23,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, I was just taking a little stroll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.27,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:18.22,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,You probably realized your \Nsubordinates were in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.72,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Huh? Did something happen to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:27.54,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,It appears I overestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:34.61,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,Given that you're their superior, I thought \Nit would be wrong not to inform you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:41.08,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,Last night at 22:00, an order for the\Nelimination of Balgo Parks was issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.89,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,While it hasn't been carried out yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.50,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,I hear Bangnyfe is already on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:50.32,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know how he works.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.21,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,At least watch out for your subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:55.87,Default,Squire,0,0,0,,Let's go, Arkvine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.22,Default,Arkvine,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:04.38,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Well, this ain't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.95,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,She's not dead, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.90,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to write up a report if she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:14.90,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.39,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Looks like you know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.03,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Guess that's no surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.36,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,But I know who you are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.32,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.70,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.43,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Bruno... Bangnyfe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:33.60,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,He's one of the Top of Horns...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:36.21,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,And the director of the Inks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:39.99,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,What the hell is he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:43.87,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Well, at least {\i1}she{\i0} knows who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.96,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve, \Npissing me off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:46.92,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,But whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:51.81,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,It's me. Set up an emergency dragon \Nblockade at Penfront Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:57.48,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Get rid of all the bystanders\Nexcept for the Wing Bind employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:02.84,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,You'll be able to tell who the Wing Bind\Nemployee is from his Piper's mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:19.09,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Detain that Wing Bind\Nemployee when you find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.97,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,He's the one behind the\Ndragon terrorist attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.35,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:31.73,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,You're the one who ordered the\Nchief to give him that mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.73,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Makes sense, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:38.60,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,A dragonclad with dragon \Npowers decides to attack
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:43.36,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,the tabloid office that\Nmade a joke at his expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:47.97,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Not that I really care if \Nit makes sense or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.88,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,You're messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:52.24,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Does that mean you framed Balgo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:54.00,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,What good will come of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.07,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Oh, plenty of good will come of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:59.50,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,At 22:00 last night,\Na punitive dragon designation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.02,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,and elimination order for\NBalgo Parks was issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:06.01,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,In just a few hours, \Nthere'll be a bounty on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:12.77,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,And whoever takes him out will go down \Nin Reverse London's history forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.83,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'll be taking him in for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.85,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,And as soon as the order goes into effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:21.04,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'll kill him on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.79,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Don't even try crying or negotiating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:27.76,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'm still working under the \NDragon Contact Prohibition Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:31.54,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,I said it before, but I don't plan\Non taking you two out, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.04,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,As long as you stay out of my way, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:36.68,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Bruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.17,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.42,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,You have the worst dye job I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.17,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,The hell did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.57,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.21,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Niiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:51.09,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Yes? I don't think I did anything \Nworthy of being scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:52.20,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.47,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I was gonna compliment \Nyou and say "good job"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:59.01,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,It didn't exactly warrant \Na compliment, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:04.14,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,I was trying to be nice\N'cause you're just lackeys,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:06.32,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,but you just had to get cocky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:09.70,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,This is definitely gonna be\Nan "accident on the job."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.44,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Guess I don't mind writing\Nup those reports after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.41,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,What're you doing, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.46,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,You're not coming at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.84,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,You dumbasses! Look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.09,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Put up a shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:30.59,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:39.85,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,N-Noel? You came to rescue me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:44.61,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,Well... I can't deny that you were\Nrescued as a result of my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.56,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:49.11,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Though I have no idea\Nwhat I've gotten myself into!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:52.37,Default,Balgo,0,0,0,,Go me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:53.78,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.07,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:06.09,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,This isn't how that usually works, but I guess \Nthat's how you Pipers learn to operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:10.13,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Are you the one who brought \NMacy to Reverse London?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.34,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Why does she have a dragon with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.68,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Couldn't just keep it to one question,\Nyou stupid little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:21.87,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,That's right. I scouted her\Nand brought her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:27.46,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,She'd found a baby dragon in\NFront London and was raising it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:31.58,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'm sure you wanted to pin\Nthat dragon on me, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:32.65,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,but it wasn't my doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:37.30,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,That woman is one of those rare people\Nborn in Front London who just happens
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.41,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,to possess a high amount of mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.17,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,She's a Watcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:49.38,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Macy's... a Watcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:53.60,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,She would've ended up in\NReverse London sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.01,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Just like you and Noel Niihashi did...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:57.87,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.94,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Don't be so on edge when \Nyou're holding your Witch Kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.44,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,What if it accidentally goes off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.40,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:16.91,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:18.91,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Marshal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.21,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,Nina, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:33.88,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Just stay calm. I'll take you \Nback to somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:41.73,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,Elly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.02,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Balgo Parks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.08,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Macy Baljure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:54.70,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,You're seriously taking those\Ntwo and trying to run from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.49,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Rickenbacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.05,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Talk about naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:21.39,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. Stop crying already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.53,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,But I left Elly behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:28.57,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I already told you we can't\Ntake the damn dragon with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.44,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,They're harmful to normal people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.04,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:37.03,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Would you stop your whining?!\NThis is exactly what I hate about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.45,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I knew it, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.95,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,You really do hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.98,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.97,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Why are you so irritating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:53.08,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,For the time being, we should be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:56.14,Default,Noel,0,0,0,,I've set up a Cloth, so they \Nshouldn't be able to find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.04,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Macy, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:10.00,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,You knew I didn't like\Nbeing in the group, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.00,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,Yeah, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:15.60,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I'm just tall, look all right in makeup,\Nand happen to be a good dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:19.37,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,So they gave me cool clothes to wear\Nand put all this cool makeup on my face,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:21.49,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,and I ended up as this cool icon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:26.34,Default,Ninny,0,0,0,,I know. That's why you quit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.58,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,No, if that's all it was,\NI would've quit a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.06,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,But I didn't quit... because you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.93,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,And if I quit, I'd become a nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:50.36,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I found that little one two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:58.19,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,She looked just like the dragons\NI'd seen in picture books and cartoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:04.70,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,Apparently, no one else could see her.\NSo I thought I was imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:15.69,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,But then she started drinking water,\Nso I figured she must be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.60,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I gave her some food, and she ate that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:25.64,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I gave her lots of different stuff to eat, but\Nshe seemed to like fruits and veggies the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:31.35,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,She didn't go to the bathroom,\Nbut she just kept getting bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:34.59,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,She started looking more \Nand more like a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.11,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,A dragon only I could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:43.33,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I suddenly felt like I was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:51.15,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I know our songs did really well, and you\Nand the other girls were amazing on stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:53.93,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,but I was the only one\Nwho wasn't myself up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.17,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,And yet, I had nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:05.93,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I'm sure no one even noticed me up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:12.89,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,But that all changed when I found Elly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:16.66,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,It felt like Elly gave me some kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:22.61,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I felt like she'd take me somewhere special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:29.42,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,Then he... Bruno came \Nto my place late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:35.67,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,He told me he needed me and my dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.87,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I finally felt like my time had come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:41.51,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,I was finally going to be \Ntaken somewhere special!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.78,Default,Macy,0,0,0,,Nina, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.58,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:56.28,Default,Bruno,0,0,0,,You guys done saying your final goodbyes?
